# XcodeGen output (regenerated by `xcodegen generate`)
# We DO commit the generated .xcodeproj so a fresh clone can open in Xcode
# without first installing xcodegen. The pbxproj is tracked.
# (Mirrors the convention used in ~/code/farkle.)
